{
  "info": {
    "name": "Simulador de Entrevistas - API",
    "description": "Colección completa del backend NestJS (PostgreSQL + MongoDB).\n\n## Cómo usar\n1. Selecciona el entorno o define la variable `base_url` (ej: http://localhost:3000).\n2. Ejecuta `Auth > Login` o `Auth > Register`: el `access_token` se guarda AUTOMÁTICAMENTE en la variable `{{jwt}}` (revisa la pestaña Scripts de cada request).\n3. Las rutas protegidas usan `{{jwt}}` en el header Authorization.\n4. Recuerda correr `npm run seed` antes de probar, para que los catálogos tengan datos.\n\nLos GET de catálogos son públicos; POST/PATCH/DELETE requieren token de ADMIN.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:3000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "jwt", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "interview_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "user_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "question_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "catalog_id", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health / Swagger",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET / (health)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": [""] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET /api/docs (Swagger UI)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/docs", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "docs"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST /auth/register",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.access_token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('jwt', res.access_token);",
                  "  console.log('Token guardado en {{jwt}}');",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"nuevo@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"firstName\": \"John\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Doe\",\n  \"seniorityLevel\": \"mid\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/register", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["auth", "register"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /auth/login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.access_token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('jwt', res.access_token);",
                  "  console.log('Token guardado en {{jwt}}');",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('status 200/201', () => pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([200, 201]));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"nuevo@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["auth", "login"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /auth/login (credenciales inválidas -> 401)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"nuevo@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"clave-incorrecta\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["auth", "login"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Users (JWT)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /users",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{jwt}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/users", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["users"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET /users/:id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{jwt}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/users/{{user_id}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["users", "{{user_id}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "PATCH /users/:id",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{jwt}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"firstName\": \"Nombre Actualizado\"\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/users/{{user_id}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["users", "{{user_id}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "DELETE /users/:id",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{jwt}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/users/{{user_id}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["users", "{{user_id}}"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
